<br>
CHECK OFF LIST <br>
<br>
ITEMS NEEDED <br>
Some form of Enduring Breath <br>
Rations &amp; Water as camping take awhile <br>
Lots of friends for the big fights <br>
<br>
Step One: Obtain the Orb of Frozen Water <br>
GROUP SIZE: Solo, I used a tank and druid <br>
* Go to Lake Rathetear <br>
* Go to Island with 3 Aviaks loc (2800, 150) <br>
* Swim under Island <br>
* Go to cave entrance loc (2831, -912, -221) <br>
* Go to Aquagoblin Tower (note: Wolfform = no aggro) <br>
* Kill all 4 Aquagoblin on top of tower - Do not use AE – Deep is tough <br>
* Kill Lord Begurgle in Lake Rathe - 28 minute spawn timer <br>
* Loot “Lord Bergurgle's Crown” <br>
* Give it to Shmendrik Lavawalker 3600, 0 - 15 minute spawn timer <br>
* Let Natasha Whitewater kill Shmendrik <br>
* Kill “a spirit of flame” <br>
* Loot &quot;Damaged Goblin Crown&quot; <br>
* Give it to Natasha Whitewater <br>
* Receive &quot;Ornate Sea Shell (I)&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Timorous Deep <br>
* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227) <br>
* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -372<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
* Swim to the other side <br>
* Head right keeping the wall on your left <br>
* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307 <br>
* Enter the Hidden Oasis <br>
* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier <br>
* Give &quot;Ornate Sea Shell(I)&quot; to Omat Vastsea <br>
* Receive &quot;Coral Statue of Tarew&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Temple of Solusek Ro <br>
GROUP SIZE: 1 group <br>
* Go through the big door and left <br>
* Go to balcony and up some stairs <br>
* Make a left there is a room with throne loc (326,38,29) <br>
* Practice route to the zone or have CoH’r <br>
* Have puller come with you <br>
* Announce you are pulling the Priest <br>
* Give Coral Statue of Tarew to “a seeker” You want the guy one <br>
Note:Spawns 9am, Despawns 9pm (game time) - Seeker is a guy <br>
* Kill Plasmatic Priest <br>
* Loot &quot;Blood Soaked Plasmatic Priest Robe&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Solusek A <br>
GROUP SIZE: Solo, I used a tank and druid <br>
* Go the room has pit in it loc (-796, -366) <br>
* Kill Lord Gimblox - 19 min. spawn, PH &quot;Lg Fire Goblin&quot; or &quot;fire goblin shaman&quot; <br>
* Loot &quot;Lord Gimblox's Signet Ring&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Timorous Deep <br>
* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227) <br>
* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -372<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
* Swim to the other side <br>
* Head right keeping the wall on your left <br>
* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307 <br>
* Enter the Hidden Oasis <br>
* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier <br>
* Give Omat &quot;Blood Soaked Plasmatic Priest Robe&quot; <br>
* Receive &quot;Orb of Frozen Water&quot; <br>
* Find Natasha Whitewater in building behind Omat <br>
* Give &quot;Lord Gimblox's Signet Ring&quot; to Natasha Whitewater <br>
* Receive &quot;Ornate Sea Shell (II)&quot; <br>
<br>
Step Two: Obtain the Orb of Clear Water <br>
GROUP SIZE: 3-5 Groups Depending on Level <br>
* Go to Burning Woods <br>
* Give &quot;Ornate Sea Shell (II)&quot; to Naxot Deepwater loc (3400, -2150) <br>
* Receive &quot;Message to Natasha&quot;. <br>
* Kill Ixiblat Fer <br>
* Loot &quot;Sceptre of Ixiblat Fer&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Chardok <br>
GROUP SIZE: 3-5 Groups Depending on Level <br>
* Kill Overking Bathezid Di'Zok <br>
* Loot &quot;Singed Scroll&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Timorous Deep <br>
* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227) <br>
* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -372<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
* Swim to the other side <br>
* Head right keeping the wall on your left <br>
* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307 <br>
* Enter the Hidden Oasis <br>
* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier <br>
* Give &quot;Sceptre of Ixiblat Fer&quot; and &quot;Singed Scroll&quot; to Omat Vastsea <br>
* Receive &quot;Orb of Clear Water&quot; <br>
* Find Natasha Whitewater in building behind Omat <br>
* Give &quot;Message to Natasha&quot; to Natasha Whitewater <br>
* Receive &quot;Shimmering Pearl&quot; <br>
<br>
Step Three: Obtain the Orb of Vapor <br>
* Go to Nagafen’s Lair <br>
GROUP SIZE: Solo <br>
* Go towards the Fire Giants Castle <br>
* Across the ramp there is a ledge Under that banner, Zordak Ragefire will spawn <br>
* Give &quot;Shimmering Pearl&quot; to Zordak Ragefire <br>
* You now have the Swirling Pearl <br>
* If you do not have the &quot;Boxof Binding&quot; from the Warder, you will get one <br>
<br>
* Go to Skyfire Mountains <br>
GROUP SIZE: 3-5 Groups Depending on Level <br>
* Go to LOC p3200 n3200 - Big Dragon statue, he spawns in front <br>
* Go to Sky Fire Mountains <br>
*Hail the Warden <br>
* Receive &quot;Box of Binding&quot; <br>
* Kill random mobs in Sky Fire Mountains, obtain 4 pearlescent fragments <br>
* Combine 4 pearlescent fragments in the “Box of Binding” <br>
* Hand box into Warder <br>
* Receive a Seal <br>
* The human form of RF will now spawn. <br>
* Kill Zordak Ragefire, the human level 55 <br>
* Kill Zordakalicus Ragefire, Dragon Level 60 <br>
* Loot &quot;Impure Heart of Ragefire&quot; NO DROP Container <br>
* Place the &quot;Swirling Pearl&quot; inside Heart <br>
* Place the &quot;Seal&quot; in Heart with pearl <br>
* Click Combine, Container becomes &quot; Heart of Ragefire&quot; <br>
<br>
* Go to Timorous Deep <br>
* Go to Island loc (-11567, -2227) <br>
* Swim through cave entrance at loc (-11530, -372<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
* Swim to the other side <br>
* Head right keeping the wall on your left <br>
* Swim through the other cave entrance at (-11336, -1307 <br>
* Enter the Hidden Oasis <br>
* Find Omat Vastsea on Pier <br>
* Give &quot;Heart of Zordak Ragefire&quot; to Omat Vastsea <br>
* Receive &quot;Orb of Vapor&quot; <br>
<br>
Step Four: Obtain the Orb of the Triumvirate <br>
* Find Jhassad Oceanson on the beach by a tree <br>
* Give &quot;Orb of Frozen Water&quot;, &quot;Orb of Clear Water&quot;, <br>
and &quot;Orb of Vapor&quot; to Jhassad Oceanson <br>
<br>
Step Five: Obtain the Water Sprinkler of Nem Ankh <br>
* Be patient, Avatar of Water end up beside Jhassad <br>
* Give &quot;Orb of the Triumvirate&quot; to Avatar of Water <br>
* Receiving the Water Sprinkler of Nem Ankh <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=31.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=31.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm8.threadControl?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub78.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="walkersofvazaellefrm4">General<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm10">Screenshots<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm19">Polling Station<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm23">Computer and Technical Issues<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm7">Charter<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm8">Guides<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm3">Private<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm2">Raids<option value="walkersofvazaellefrm15">Epics<option value="walkersofvazael